{"word":"G987 - βλασφημέω - blasphēméō - blas-fay-meh'-o - Blaspheme","slug":"G987","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βλασφημέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>blasphēméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>blas-fay-meh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Blaspheme"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B2;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03C3;&#x03C6;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - blasphe&#x0304;meo&#x0304;</b> - <i>blas-fay-meh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G989\">G989</a>; to <i>vilify</i>; specifically to <i>speak impiously:</i> - (speak) blaspheme (-er, -mously, -my), defame, rail on, revile, speak evil."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G988\">G988</a>, <a href=\"#/G989\">G989</a>"}]}